The tumulus is located on a hill about 150 meters northeast of Harumakita Elementary School, approximately a 20-minute walk from [[:en:Ōmuta Station|Ōmuta Station]] on the [[JR Kyushu]] [[Kagoshima Main Line]].<ref name="Shiseki"/>
